    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB) for use with network management protocols in the Internet community.  In particular, this specifies objects for managing virtual machines controlled by a hypervisor (a.k.a.  virtual machine monitor).&lt;/p&gt;</t>
